@startuml
title InsightsRadar v1 - End-to-End Digest Lifecycle

actor User
participant "Cron Trigger" as Cron
participant "Worker: Ingest Flow" as Ingest
participant "Cloudflare Blog RSS" as RSS
database "D1 Metadata DB" as D1
queue "Cloudflare Queue" as Q
participant "Worker: Queue Consumer" as Digest
participant "Workers AI\n(Primary/Fallback)" as AI
collections "R2 Artifact Store" as R2
participant "Worker API (/api/*)" as API
participant "Web App (React)" as Web

== Ingestion ==
Cron -> Ingest: hourly scheduled run
Ingest -> RSS: fetch RSS feed
RSS --> Ingest: feed items
Ingest -> Ingest: filter by start date + ingestion mode
Ingest -> D1: upsert metadata (status=pending)
Ingest -> Q: enqueue new/changed canonical URLs

== Digest Processing ==
Q -> Digest: deliver article job
Digest -> D1: fetch article + keywords
Digest -> AI: generate digests (primary model)
alt primary succeeds
  AI --> Digest: valid JSON digest payload
else primary fails/retries exhausted
  Digest -> AI: switch to fallback model
  AI --> Digest: success OR terminal failure
end

alt digest success
  Digest -> R2: write source/level1/level2/processing artifacts
  Digest -> D1: update status=processed\nword counts + model fields + keys
else digest failure
  Digest -> D1: update status=digest_failed\nfailure_reason + retry_count
end

== UI Read Path ==
User -> Web: open app
Web -> API: GET /api/articles?cursor=...
API -> D1: query processed tiles
D1 --> API: items + nextCursor
API --> Web: tile feed payload

Web -> API: GET /api/articles/summary?id=...
API -> D1: fetch summary payload
D1 --> API: summary data
API --> Web: summary response

Web -> API: GET /api/articles/detail?id=...
API -> D1: fetch detail payload
D1 --> API: detail data
API --> Web: detail response

== Manual Ops ==
User -> API: POST /api/admin/reprocess (token)
API -> Q: enqueue manual_reprocess

User -> API: POST /api/admin/backfill (token,start_date)
API -> RSS: scan feed for eligible posts
API -> Q: enqueue manual_backfill jobs

@enduml
